    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You summon a ball of fury in your palm. Make a Ranged Taijutsu or Ninjutsu attack against a creature within range. On a hit, you deal 2d12 Force Damage.</p><p><strong>Empower:</strong> When you cast this Jutsu, you may expend a Ki Die. If you do, double its range and add an additional die of damage.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank above D-Rank, this Jutsu costs 3 more chakra, and you may make an additional attack against a different creature in range.</p>",
